\det B=a
A = [a_{ij}] \in \mathcal{M}(n,n; K), \ \det A=a, \ \ c \in K, c \neq0
B= [b_{ij}] \in \mathcal{M}(n,n; K), \ \ b_{ij}=c^{i-j}a_{ij}, \ \ \ i,j \in \{ 1,2,\dots,n\}
\det B
\det A
B=\begin{pmatrix}c^1\\&c^2\\&&\ddots\\&&&c^n\end{pmatrix}A\begin{pmatrix}c^1\\&c^2\\&&\ddots\\&&&c^n\end{pmatrix}^{-1}.
